.Trashes
.VolumeIcon.icns
.com.apple.timemachine.donotpresent
.AppleDB
.AppleDesktop
Network Trash Folder
Temporary Items
.apdisk

# Linux
*~
.fuse_hidden*
.directory
.Trash-*
.nfs*

